OL,3,CWorkers at steel giant Tata to strike
OL,4,Cin protest against job losses
OL,6,FWorkers at steel giant Tata are to
OL,7,Fstrike in protest at the company's
OL,8,Fplans to close blast furnaces with the
OL,9,Floss of jobs.
OL,11,FUnite said around 1,500 of its members
OL,12,Fbased in Port Talbot and Llanwern,
OL,13,Fsouth Wales, will begin an indefinite
OL,14,Fstrike on July 8.
OL,16,FUnite members are already working to
OL,17,Frule and banning overtime but the
OL,18,Fannouncement of a strike is a
OL,19,Fsignificant escalation.
