OL,6,F"Our members will not stand by while
OL,7,Fthis immensely wealthy conglomerate
OL,8,Ftries to throw Port Talbot and
OL,9,FLlanwern on the scrapheap so it can
OL,10,Fboost its operations abroad.
OL,12,F"They know south Wales is ideally
OL,13,Fplaced to take advantage of the coming
OL,14,Fboom in green steel ` if the right
OL,15,Fchoices are made.
