OL,3,CWorkers at steel giant Tata to strike
OL,4,Cin protest against job losses
OL,6,F"Our existing steelmaking assets are
OL,7,Fnear the end of their life, are
OL,8,Foperationally unstable and causing
OL,9,Funsustainable losses of #1 million a
OL,10,Fday. This is why preparations to close
OL,11,Fthe blast furnaces and associated
OL,12,Fplants in Port Talbot are unchanged.
OL,14,F"However, if the safety and stability
OL,15,Fof our operations are put at risk by
OL,16,Fthis action, we will be forced to
OL,17,Faccelerate those closure plans.
