OL,3,CWorkers at steel giant Tata to strike
OL,4,Cin protest against job losses
OL,6,F"After extensive negotiations with our
OL,7,Funions we substantially improved our
OL,8,Fsupport offering for affected
OL,9,Femployees ` the most generous package
OL,10,Fin our history. Rather than taking
OL,11,Fstrike action, we would have expected
OL,12,FUnite to put our improved offer to its
OL,13,Fmembers, as previously accepted by all
OL,14,Funions, including Unite."
OL,16,FCommunity and the GMB unions are also
OL,17,Fcampaigning against the plans but have
OL,18,Fruled out taking industrial action
OL,19,Fbefore the General Election.
