OL,6,FThe company offered an enhanced
OL,7,Fredundancy package to workers affected
OL,8,Fby the plans, but this was reduced
OL,9,Fafter Unite started its industrial
OL,10,Faction earlier this week.
OL,12,FThe strike announcement comes two
OL,13,Fyears to the day since members of the
OL,14,FRMT rail union went on strike, kicking
OL,15,Foff a wave of walkouts by hundreds of
OL,16,Fthousands of workers over pay and
OL,17,Fconditions, including nurses, teachers
OL,18,Fand junior doctors.
